{"tid":2055051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國震音哨牙佬終極叛國！譚詠麟竟揸BNO出埠飛美國！？","createTime":"2020-06-07T15:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T13:15:11.000Z","uid":82917,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b5c3275a1380154bd7be646c124c4e8d0566c1","tid":2055051,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舊聞重溫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n心繫祖國的譚詠麟，六月底出席撐警活動後，便由「譚校長」榮升為「藍校長」。口口聲聲呼籲大家「不要受外來勢力影響」，但阿倫似乎「口裡說不，身體卻很誠實」。與很多香港人一樣，原來「藍校長」也是BNO的粉絲。早前見他與紅顏知己Wendy出埠過關時，手持的竟然是這本紅色皮的英國國民海外護照，俗稱BNO。未知向來深愛祖國的牙倫今次又如何解釋呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_694780_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_694780_0&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3Kf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=597da9b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_694780_0&h=6f4784a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_694780_0</a>"},{"pid":"b631ce7f772ef4b3fcb43d6cb8eee0875dcf0346","tid":2055051,"uid":82917,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"死撲街谭咏伦、、，我作了距噶粉絲好奈。😅旦沒捻到,, 距竟持..外國護照😅 还要唔要脸啰？。吊巨楼某😡❌ 吃碗面反碗低，距噶所作所為实在令人发旨！😭😭😭 这反中乱港的🈲臭傻逼。！"},{"pid":"90eeb82972f334165bacdf6b3b504977432816f1","tid":2055051,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce66211b967f77f58c5d3c40b284e1a606ccc45a","tid":2055051,"uid":105298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:59:15.000Z","msg":"佢個仔係美國讀大學<br />\n有無得踢佢返支那讀？"},{"pid":"110d812c430fdedfaa5e37861cec19d5e5a33b01","tid":2055051,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"各位蓝友，一定要低製哩个吃里扒外噶反骨老😡😡💪🏻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ohyt4V9.png\" data-thumbna